1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Funny thing, when I was 7, I made a boat out of mismatched toys and it sort of held together.

2
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,720
Not that it matters, but building that way stuck with me.

3
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:16,560
Quick fixes, duct tape elegance.

4
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:24,400
So when people ask about ownership of systems, I say I built parts of things, stitched services

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:28,400
together and occasionally owned a small feature.

6
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:33,120
Sometimes I talk about entire projects because it's simpler to tell a story than to read

7
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:34,880
the commit history.

8
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:35,960
It gets messy.

